{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"955028bef8","title":"复刘少奇、高岗、王称祥电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1c9a180659","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"955028bef8"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"173f71109b","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"955028bef8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东复刘少奇、高岗、王豫祥电的主要内容。"},{"id":"1b60aef82e","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"955028bef8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柯兄，指柯瓦家夫，当时任苏联铁道部副部长、中长路苏方负责人。1949年4月从东北到达北平，后接替阿洛夫负责中共与苏共的联系。"}],"contents":[{"id":"05c35d4246","type":"title","text":"复刘少奇、高岗、王橡祥电\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"955028bef8"},{"id":"173f71109b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们完全同意苏中两方组织共同委员会来把借款和定货等问题具体化；但由于我们全国经济机关方开始成立，地区不断扩大，专家缺乏，材料缺乏，故目前实无法提出全部货单。可否商请联共中央同意将共同委员会设在中国，由柯兄先带主要专家来华与我们共同商定全部或主要部分货单。如斯大林同意先派人来华组织共同委员会，请柯兄最好先带铁路、电力、钢铁、煤矿、煤油矿、军事等专家同来。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"955028bef8"}],"page":{"id":"d9518a723d","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"955028bef8","start":109,"end":109}}}},"__N_SSG":true}